# Mext

Mext is an prompt template extension for LLM (large language model).

## Syntax

{@for syntax in syntaxes}
### {syntax[name]}

Template:
```mext
{@import syntax[template] as template}
{template}
```

Given params:
```json
{@import syntax[params] as params}
{@format json params}
```

Produce:
```markdown
{@import syntax[result] as result}
{result}
```
{@endfor}
